    "dc25b428-6fdb-4bea-b22c-750a75858f25": {
      "type": "dynamic-testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "template--14842501464149__dc25b428-6fdb-4bea-b22c-750a75858f25-testimonial-1": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Grille.png",
            "star_rating": "5",
            "text": "<p><strong>Painted front bumper</strong></p><p><em>Unbelievable, unpacked the boxed bumper, placed in the sun on the shipping box and like magic it opened up and reshaped itself as the company claimed. Paint was a perfect match. Can’t thank you guys enough. Got to save hundreds over doing it any other way.</em></p>",
            "author": "<p>Kenneth R.</p>"
          }
        },
        "6dc98bfe-9b50-4ff6-8d8d-2e9197fe80fd": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Front_Bumper_5.png",
            "star_rating": "5",
            "text": "<p><strong>Quick Delivery & Exactly What I Wanted</strong></p><p>I was a little spectacle about purchasing a bumper from this site due to lack of reviews. This was the only place (other than $520+ from two other sites) that I could find an OEM bumper for my car. It was delivered after a week and packaged very well. I definitely recommend purchasing from here!</p>",
            "author": "<p>Caroline O.</p>"
          }
        },
        "6f396d9c-0e38-4e8d-959a-ef1c6d1aadc1": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Front_Bumper_b8e6c2e9-01d5-49b2-8455-47ab49382965.png",
            "star_rating": "5",
            "text": "<p><strong>Was perfect</strong></p><p>I ordered a bumper cover for my 2013 Veloster. The price was awesome, shipping was fast, the quality was excellent, the paint match-up was exact. I am very pleased. I will definitely be using Partify in the future.</p>",
            "author": "<p>Russell B.</p>"
          }
        },
        "6c2aae5e-a98c-4c26-bad6-14f5f90d3873": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Front_Bumper_6.png",
            "star_rating": "4.5",
            "text": "<p><strong>Great product perfect fit excellent color match</strong></p><p>I am very pleased with the quality of my order. The product has a perfect color match and good fit. Easy to install no issues whatsoever. I have done both the right and left fenders. Very Happy with the staff and the manner in which they were willing to help me with the courier issue. I would order from here again.</p>",
            "author": "<p>Erwin G.</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--14842501464149__dc25b428-6fdb-4bea-b22c-750a75858f25-testimonial-2": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Truck.png",
            "star_rating": "5",
            "text": "<p><strong>Would buy again!</strong></p><p>Was very impressed with paint quality and packaging</p>",
            "author": "<p>Clay R.</p>"
          }
        },
        "template--14842501464149__dc25b428-6fdb-4bea-b22c-750a75858f25-testimonial-3": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Fender.png",
            "star_rating": "4.5",
            "text": "<p><strong>2018 Dodge Durango Fender</strong></p><p>The shipment was fast and the fender showed up wrapped really well and the paint matched up perfectly. Thank you.</p>",
            "author": "<p>Jerry S.</p>"
          }
        },
        "96713aef-30ec-4a19-9cfe-12391f29fcff": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Bumper.png",
            "star_rating": "5",
            "text": "<p><strong>Fantastic Product</strong></p><p>I’ve never ordered from Partify before so I was skeptical of the end product but I was pleasantly surprised at the quality! The paint on the fender I ordered is now nicer than the rest of the paint on my car!</p>",
            "author": "<p>Mitchell B.</p>"
          }
        },
        "4aa751ac-32cf-4956-97b7-23da182a481c": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Front_Bumper_2.png",
            "star_rating": "5",
            "text": "<p><strong>Fast shipping. Good quality car part.</strong></p><p>The item looks great and fits perfectly in my car. The shipping was fast as well.</p>",
            "author": "<p>Maverick</p>"
          }
        },
        "351ca8df-8262-4df9-af2e-7351537afce1": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Front_Bumper_4.png",
            "star_rating": "4.5",
            "text": "<p><strong>100% color match! I appreciate it!</strong></p><p>The fit is amazing just like the original. The color match is 100%. Accurate. Thanks for a quality product.</p>",
            "author": "<p>Tibby G.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
